{"tid":596759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文壇才子】台作家李敖腦癌逝世 享年82歲","createTime":"2018-03-18T03:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T05:21:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac900b5176e71603eb67fba3f0b53706ebd5c75","tid":596759,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/115601_f7914c017f8463554b8bc8a5ebdbb357.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F115601_f7914c017f8463554b8bc8a5ebdbb357.png&h=8212bc72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣著名作家李敖罹患腦癌，日前多次傳出病危消息，其家屬今早透過台北榮民總醫院發佈新聞稿，確認李敖已於今早10時59分安然離世，終年82歲。<br />\n<br />\n根據台北榮民總醫院的新聞稿，李敖於2015年7月因步態不穩至本院求診，經診斷為腦幹腫瘤。去年10月1日，李敖再度因肺炎入院，治療後感染病況穩定。其後腦部磁振造影發現，原先疾病有惡化趨勢，院方有鑑於李敖年事已高等身體狀況，因而採取保守治療。<br />\n<br />\n自去年11月初起，李敖開始接受標靶藥物治療後，病況漸為好轉。但今年1月底起，標靶藥效漸失，病況急速惡化，雖肺部感染在投藥後趨穩，但電腦斷層顯現腦瘤病況惡化合併水腦加劇。近日病況轉危，李敖於今日上午10時59分安然離世，享壽82歲。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180318/57962518%20%20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57962518%2520%2520&d=XioBUHAkMQFiHr5iJCa0czACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=6a0a9881\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57962518%2520%2520&h=c8a554d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180318/57962518%20%20</a>"},{"pid":"34e9d6f969f0d799b05558d491aafb21e2c25508","tid":596759,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"估唔到"},{"pid":"941932a85a9f8f801dd7dbcf967c59a379472967","tid":596759,"uid":29804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"年輕時反對國民黨獨裁統治<br />\n解嚴後轉為支持共產黨"},{"pid":"3145a79932a8226c438d6b3ab120ab9272c7e711